# Problematic query
SPARQL {
DELETE { ?s ?p ?o . ?s1 ?p1 ?s . }
FROM <http://abc.io/test/ontology/classes>
WHERE {
  ?s ?p ?o . OPTIONAL { ?s1 ?p1 ?s . }
  ?s <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> * <http://test1.com/test1> .
}
};


Actual result of last query:
Query result:
callret-0ANY
Delete from <http://abc.io/test/ontology/classes>, 2 (or less) triples -- done
No. of rows in result: 1

Expected result of last query:
Query result:
callret-0ANY
Delete from <http://abc.io/test/ontology/properties>, 11 (or less) triples -- done
No. of rows in result: 1

