<http://test1.com/test3>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf>	<http://test1.com/test2>.
<http://abc.io/test/ontology/12345>	<http://schema.org/identifier>	"12345".
<http://test1.com/test1>	<http://schema.org/identifier>	"id1".
<http://test1.com/test2>	<http://schema.org/identifier> "id2".
<http://test1.com/test3>	<http://schema.org/identifier> "id3".
